68e48a0185751d24eecb194b8efd7028c8b590f3

```cpp
// Leave message in the transport for when the socket is available.
// v2 transport would also require waiting for the handshake to complete
```

With v2 I assume we can't even call `GetBytesToSend` before the handshake?

