comments.body:
According to `developer-notes.md` annotations in function declaration (`EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(!m_cs_recv)`) should be combined with run-time asserts in function definitions (`AssertLockNotHeld(m_cs_recv)`). So, this code should be:

```cpp
void SetReceiveVersion(int nVersionIn) override EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(!m_cs_recv)
{
    AssertLockNotHeld(m_cs_recv);
    LOCK(m_cs_recv);
```

I opened https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/27116 to relax that since it is redundant.

